'''Cosmi Americo & Figlio''' is an Italian [[shotgun]] manufacturer located in [[Ancona]], [[Italy]]. The company manufactures [[Semi-automatic shotgun|semi-automatic]] [[shotgun]]s under the name Cosmi. Only approximately 7,500 guns have been manufactured since 1930, and individual guns are unique enough that parts are often not interchangeable.<ref name=bluebook>{{Cite book | authorlink= | coauthors= | title=Blue Book of Gun Values: 29th Edition | date= | publisher=Blue Book Publications | location= | isbn=1-886768-75-7 | pages=619}} </ref> Each part is individually serial numbered. The shotgun is available in three calibers:12, 16 and 20.
